Title: Walls
Plot: Harry investigates the death of a college student which leads him to a most unusual ring of thieves.  A group of students is using magick to commit a series of impossible thefts, and Harry must stop them quickly.  Not only because what they are doing is wrong, but also because the magick will eventually kill them all.
GuestStars: Odeen  Eccleston,  Steve Byers,  Kerry Dorey,  Nathan Stephenson,  Tyrone Savage
